        <message_html><![CDATA[<p>Hello ${caller_id},</p>
<p style="margin: 6.0pt 0in .0001pt 0in;">Attached to this email and listed below are shipping transactions that were orphaned on your POS system and must be researched within 24 hours of receipt of this email.</p>
<ol>
<li>Locate all packing slips for the dates listed below. &nbsp;(<em>Packing slip example is provided at the bottom of this email.</em>)</li>
<li>Pull those packing slips that match the sales person number, the workstation ID listed below (<em>workstation ID means back office workstation, register or mistore device number</em>), and the number of units for each UPC.</li>
<li>If this shipment WAS NOT canceled, please go to the incident by clicking this&nbsp;${URI}&nbsp;and attach a copy of all packing slips that match the transaction criteria attached/below.&nbsp;</li>
<li>If this shipment WAS canceled, please click: &nbsp;<span style="text-align: start;">${mail_script:orphaned_trans_link_script}</span></li>
<li>A confirmation screen will appear&nbsp;once you have completed the request.</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Orphaned Transactions To Research (also attached in this email):</strong></p>
